title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table that contains a highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.

Notes: Please provide more specific details about the report and the table (e.g., the data being exported, the type of highlight/map being used) to aid in reproducing the issue accurately.
OB: When trying to export data from a table containing a highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported successfully from the table with a highlight/map without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table that contains a highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
